		<hr size="1">Looking at some other posts I found a formula for determining your maximum damage for melee weapons. It is (Skill lvl + Strength + Character lvl) * Weapon Dam /100.<BR>Tested the formula out and it is bang on for my melee weapons damage. What I was wondering what the formula is for bows?  Modified the above formula and I can't come up with a combo the fits with what I'm doing for damage now. </P><P>Any info would be great!</P><P>Anexander Arrowstorm<BR>26th Season Ranger of Kelethin<BR>Quellious<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
